          "issue": "M adaptive suspension noise when cold during the first seconds",
          "frequency": "occasional",
          "cost": "Usually resolved with lubrication, ~€150"
        },
        {
          "issue": "Minor BMW OS glitches after software updates",
          "frequency": "occasional",
          "cost": "Resolved under warranty or via OTA update"
        }
      ],
      "ownerReviews": [
        {
          "quote": "I have covered 40,000 km with my M5 and it still excites me every time I start it. Fuel consumption is high, but the smile it puts on my face is worth every cent.",
          "author": "Marcus T.",
          "location": "Munich, Germany",
          "ownsSince": "2024",
          "rating": 9.5
        },
        {
          "quote": "I use it for business trips and weekend getaways. In Comfort mode it is as quiet as a 7 Series, but press M Mode and it transforms.",
          "author": "Sophie L.",
          "location": "Lyon, France",
          "ownsSince": "2025",
          "rating": 9
        }
      ],
      "satisfactionRating": 9.2
    },
    "fr": {
      "ownerReviews": [
        {
          "quote": "J'ai parcouru 40 000 km avec ma M5 et elle m'excite encore à chaque démarrage. La consommation est élevée, mais le sourire qu'elle me procure vaut chaque centime.",
